Titolo: Nail'd

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: Nail'd is an off-road arcade racing game developed by Techland for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360. Nail'd was released on 30 November 2010 in North America and later on in 2011 in the PAL region and Japan. The game focuses on ATV and dirtbike racing, with an emphasis on speed and verticality.
Nail'd is published by Deep Silver and Cyberfront and features a soundtrack including bands such as Rise Against, Slipknot and Queens of the Stone Age.